    <briefdescription>
<para>Wrappers around various support functions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Simplified NFA API, used in binding to call NFA algorithms.</para>
<para>In particular, this mostly includes operations and checks, that do not return Automaton, but instead take resulting automaton as pointer (e.g. <computeroutput>void f(Nfa* result, const Nfa&amp; lhs, const Nfa&amp; rhs)</computeroutput>). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
